  "title": "Floor / Host / Cashier #FT and PT Welcome #town #5day #Monthly Store Incentives #Town / Airport",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for passionate, dedicated individuals to join us on this journey of bringing various cuisines to more guests. As an organisation, we believe in growing together and offer a supportive team culture, career development opportunities to help you build a rewarding future in the F&B industry. </p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Welcome and seat guests professionally</li><li>Manage reservations & guest inquiries</li><li>Handle billing, cashiering & POS system</li><li>Ensure front desk cleanliness & efficiency</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Pleasant personality and good communication skills</li><li>Experience in customer service / cashiering preferred</li><li>Able to work shifts, weekends & PH</li></ul><p><strong>✨ What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li>Staff meals, uniforms & training provided</li><li>Career advancement with expanding brand</li><li>Incentives & supportive team culture</li></ul><p><em>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</em></p>",
