    "description": "<p>Join Our New Restaurant in Clarke Quay Central – Exciting Opportunities Available!<br>\n<br>\nOur mission is to bring the rich, flavorful heritage cuisine to life with modern touches, offering a unique and unforgettable dining experience.<br>\n<br>\nWe are looking for passionate, dedicated, and customer-focused individuals to join our growing team. Whether you have a love for culinary arts, exceptional service skills, or a desire to contribute to an exciting new venture, we would love to hear from you.<br>\n<br>\nWhy Join Us?<br>\n<br>\nBe part of a brand-new concept in one of Singapore's most iconic dining destinations.<br>\nWork with a dynamic, creative team committed to delivering excellence.<br>\nOpportunities for career growth in an exciting, fast-paced environment.<br>\nCompetitive salary and benefits.<br>\nIf you are eager to contribute to a restaurant that celebrates culture, creativity, and authentic flavors, come join us as we embark on this exciting culinary journey!<br>\n</p>",
